content: dutch dunes for this pattern i made 2 different versions the first one is made with cotton kings twirls in the color ocean jasper and after blocking it measures about 69 x 140 cm the second wrap i made with stylecraft life changes in the color roses and after blocking it measures about 88 x 180 cm of course you can use any yarn or colors you like but it will affect the size of the wrap if you need help making this pattern or want to show your result join the facebook group luby s crochet corner copyright lubys eva van gerner all rights reserved this pattern is for personal use only you do not have the right to claim this pattern as your own nor to sell the pattern or share the file in any form you have no right to make video tutorials of this pattern you may sell your finished item but you may not use my pictures to promote the item
